"tsetse fly control area" means an area defined and declared in terms of section
three to be a tsetse fly control area;
"vehicle" means any carriage or conveyance for use upon land or water, or any
aircraft.
(As amended by No. 11 of 1956, No. 41 of 1959
and No. 25 of 1969)
